				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p126625">Re: YCPU: an imaginary 16-bit processor.</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=126625#p126625"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Mon Mar 10, 2014 1:13 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
